entry.content: Update... This is so surreal. My doctor was 10 minutes away from being able to give me a refill, and 10 minutes later, she wasn't legally allowed. This is a lot, please don't forget to take care of your mental health during this time. Don't be afraid to reach out to one another, or to me. I will do everything I can to help. I love you all so much. I'm so sorry. #fyp #trans
